    <constraint source="spec AC-3c">PlaybookBuilder UI palette displays the Tool; property panel shows configurable allow-list source binding via EntityNameValidatorForm.tsx.</constraint>
    <constraint source="project">Upsert pattern (Owner Q&amp;A spec line 343) — idempotent.</constraint>
