  <notes>Spec references: FR-3 (lines 116-122), AC-3a + AC-3c (lines 119, 121), Owner Q&amp;A on 141 confirmation (line 342). Depends on tasks 002 (enum), 003 (executor + tests), 004 (form). If any of those are not ✅ in TASK-INDEX, escalate before deploying — a deployed row referencing a non-existent ActionType in BFF will fail at playbook-engine resolution.</notes>

